description: This skill records the most recent time you or someone in your household fed your dogs.  You tell it when you feed your dogs, and someone else can then later ask when the dogs were last fed so they will know if the dogs still need to be fed.  This eliminates the risk of the dogs missing a meal or being overfed.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, tell dog buddy that I fed the dogs
Alexa, ask dog buddy when did I feed the dogs
Alexa, tell dog buddy that I fed the dogs ten minutes ago
name: Dog Buddy
shortDescription: Skill to record when you last fed your dogs, so your housemates will know if they have been fed recently or if they still need food.
